description:
What happens when we die? As Adventists, we believe God is the source of life, so human immortality depends on God’s gift of life. 

For the full video about the 26th Fundamental Belief, “The State of the Dead,” paste this link into your browser: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r6o8IbTvZXc
